ympic Games | date=February 2008 | publisher=International Olympic Committee | pages=1\u20132 | accessdate=2 May 2009\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Buying the Games\">\n{{cite news | title=Buying the Games | last=Rowlatt | first=Justin | publisher=BBC | date=29 July 2004 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/programmes/panorama/3937425.stm | accessdate=16 April 2009\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"television\">\n{{cite web\n |title=Issues of the Olympic Games\n |website=Olympic Primer\n |publisher=LA84 Foundation of Los Angeles\n |url=http://www.la84foundation.org/6oic/primer_text2.htm\n |accessdate=30 March 2009\n |url-status=dead\n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090425100112/http://www.la84foundation.org/6oic/primer_text2.htm\n |archivedate=25 April 2009\n |df=\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ratings\">\n{{cite news | title=A Surprise Winner at the Olympic Games in Beijing: NBC | last1=Carter | first1=Bill | last2=Sandomir | first2=Richard | work=The New York Times | date=17 August 2008 | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/18/sports/olympics/18nbc.html?ref=business | accessdate=2 April 2009\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"olympicsymbols\">\n{{cite web\n |url=http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_1303.pdf\n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090324234949/http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_1303.pdf\n |archivedate=24 March 2009\n |title=The Olympic Symbols\n |publisher=International Olympic Committee\n |accessdate=4 February 2009\n |url-status=dead\n |df=\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"torch\">\n{{cite web\n |url=http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_655.pdf\n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090325013924/http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_655.pdf\n |archivedate=25 March 2009\n |title=The Olympic flame and the torch relay\n |website=Olympic Museum\n |publisher=International Olympic Committee\n |year=2007\n |page=6\n |accessdate=4 February 2009\n |url-status=dead\n |df=\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"OCFactSheetS\">\n{{cite web | title= Fact sheet: Opening Ceremony of the Summer Olympic Games | publisher= International Olympic Committee |date=February 2008 | url= http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_1134.pdf | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110429094114/http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_1134.pdf | archivedate= 29 April 2011 | accessdate=14 August 2008\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"OCFactSheetW\">\n{{cite web\n |title=Fact sheet: Opening Ceremony of the Winter Olympic Games\n |publisher=International Olympic Committee\n |date=February 2008\n |url=http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_1036.pdf\n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090325013925/http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_1036.pdf\n |archivedate=25 March 2009\n |accessdate=14 August 2008\n |url-status=dead\n |df=\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"OCprotocol1\">\n{{cite book\n |title=The Modern Olympic Games\n |chapter=The development of the Games \u2013 Between festival and tradition\n |publisher=International Olympic Committee\n |page=5\n |url=http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_668.pdf\n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090325013906/http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_668.pdf\n |archivedate=25 March 2009\n |chapterurl=http://multimedia.olympic.org/pdf/en_report_668.pdf#pages=5\n |accessdate=29 August 2008\n |url-status=dead\n |df=\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"otraditions\">\n{{cite news | title= Symbols and Traditions | work= USA Today | date= 12 July 1999 | url= https://www.usatoday.com/olympics/owg98/osytr03.htm | accessdate=29 August 2008\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Sports\">\n{{cite web | url=http://olympic.org/uk/sports/index_uk.asp | title=Sports | publisher=International Olympic Committee | accessdate=8 February 2009\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"recognizedsports\">\n{{cite web | url=http://www.olympic.org/uk/sports/recognized/index_uk.asp | title=Recognised Sports | publisher=International Olympic Committee | accessdate=31 March 2009\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"factsheetsports\">\n{